subtitle: today is the 21st day of the Omer which
is nobility and compassion the exercise
for today is to help the needy in a way
that strengthens their dignity you will
always know nobility and compassion
because it boosts self-esteem both the
giver and the receiver are left with a
greater sense of dignity
one day as I was driving I saw a woman
standing on a street corner holding a
sign which read please help if you can
so I brought her lunch
hi I saw you standing here and I brought
you lunch I told her you saw me
you can't see me
I can see you I said
hi my name is Joanne she told me
we spoke for a few minutes and then she
shared with me some of her wisdom
saying repeat after me
my pain today
is my strength tomorrow
I've repeated after her I smiled
she smiled
we both felt good
this is nobility and compassion
